# Hono & Honox on Bun

Before implementing routing, middleware, or validators, you MUST fetch and read:
- Index: https://hono.dev/llms.txt (or https://hono.dev/llms-full.txt if deep context is needed).

## Project specifics:
- **Architecture**: Server is in `app/server.ts`, client in `app/client.ts`. Mirror existing patterns.
- **Validation**: strictly use `@hono/zod-validator` with shared Zod schemas.
